            <title>[SOLR-343] Constraining date facets by facet.mincount</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-343</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be helpful to allow the facet.mincount parameter to work with date facets, i.e. constraining the results so that it would be possible to filter out date ranges in the results where no documents occur from the server-side. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
